description: MAG Interactive AB engages in the development of mobile game software. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 104 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2017-12-08. The firm offers free-to-play games, in which the players make in application purchases of virtual items or gameplay benefits. The Company’s portfolio comprises word games, a puzzle game and trivia games; it includes Ruzzle, Ruzzle Adventure, WordBrain, WordBrain 2, Wordalot, Potion Pop, QuizDuel, Pixduel, QuizCross and Backpacker. The games are distributed through virtual stores, such as Google Play and App Store, for operating systems Android and iOS respectively. The firm operates FEO Media AB as subsidiary.
name: MAG Interactive AB (publ)
